---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">

<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 border-t-4 border-t-blue-600 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm space-y-8">

  <div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Rod Monk</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">BSc (Hons) Pure Mathematics · Master of Engineering · BC Certified Teacher</p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      BC-certified teacher and former CTO with 25 years' experience leading AI, cloud, and
      data-intensive projects. I translate complex technical ideas into engaging, inquiry-driven
      learning while championing UDL and culturally responsive practice — including recent service
      in coastal First Nations communities. My goal is to help students see how mathematics and
      computing connect to the real world, and to empower them to thrive in a digital future.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Teaching</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
      <li>Math &amp; Computer Studies (Gr 9–12), <a href="https://lilwat.ca/citizenservices/education/xetolacw/" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">Xetolacw Community School</a>, Mount Currie, BC</li>
      <li>Math (Gr 8–12), <a href="https://www.ahousahted.com/" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">Ahousaht Education Authority</a>, Flores Island, BC</li>
      <li>Lecturer, Intro to Python, <a href="https://www.vcc.ca/" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">Vancouver Community College</a></li>
      <li>Computer Science Lecturer, <a href="https://nul.ls/" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">National University of Lesotho</a>, Lesotho, Africa</li>
      <li>Grade 13 Calculus and Grade 13 Statistics, <a href="https://www.ocdsb.ca/" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">Ottawa-Carleton District School Board</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Software Engineering Career</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
      <li>President / Principal Software Engineer, Digerati Strategies</li>
      <li>Chief Technical Officer, <a href="https://www.wencomine.com" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">Wenco International Mining Systems</a></li>
      <li>Chief &amp; Senior Software Architect, <a href="https://www.cgi.com/en/space" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">CGI Space Division</a></li>
      <li>Software Designer, <a href="https://www.esa.int/About_Us/ESOC" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">European Space Operations Centre</a>, Darmstadt, Germany</li>
      <li>Software Engineer, <a href="https://www.telesat.com/" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">Telesat</a>, Ottawa, Canada</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Education</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-700 list-disc pl-5">
      <li><a href="https://coursesforteachers.ca/bc/certificates/BCMATH" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">Post Graduate Certificate in Mathematics Education</a>, Queen's University</li>
      <li><a href="https://online.stanford.edu/programs/artificial-intelligence-professional-program" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">Artificial Intelligence Professional Program</a>, Stanford University</li>
      <li><a href="https://carleton.ca/engineering-design/future-students/graduate-programs/master-of-engineering-engineering-practice/" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">Master of Engineering</a>, Carleton University</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.sfu.ca/students/admission/programs/a-z/m/mathematics.html" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">BSc (Hons) Pure Mathematics</a>, SFU</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.sfu.ca/education/programs/teacher-ed/pdp.html" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">Professional Development Program (PDP)</a>, SFU</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Interests</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">
      Certified Toastmaster · Tennis · Pickleball · Recent reading includes
      <a href="https://www.amazon.ca/Building-Thinking-Classrooms-Mathematics-Grades/dp/1544374836" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"><em>Building Thinking Classrooms</em></a>,
      <a href="https://www.amazon.ca/Mathematical-Mindsets-Unleashing-Mathematics-Innovative/dp/1119823064" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"><em>Mathematical Mindsets</em></a>,
      <a href="https://www.amazon.ca/Mapmatics-Mathematicians-Guide-Navigating-World/dp/0674294238" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"><em>Mapmatics</em></a>, and
      <a href="https://www.amazon.ca/dp/1071969501" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"><em>Data Minds</em></a>, and
      <a href="https://www.amazon.ca/Technology-Artificial-Intelligence-Mathematics-Assessment-ebook/dp/B0FMRVXGS3/" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline"><em>Digital Technology and Artificial Intelligence in Mathematics Education Assessment</em></a>.
    </p>
  </div>

</div>

</Layout>
